Package com.payd.shooti.interfaces

Interface IGravityEntityController

All Superinterfaces:
IUpdate
All Known Subinterfaces:
IPlayerController
All Known Implementing Classes:
DumbFlyingNPCController, DumbGroundNPCController, FlyingBugNPCController, FlyingPatrolBotNPCController, GravityEntityController, GroundPetNPCController, NPCController, PathfindNPCController, PlayerController, PlayerNPCController, VehicleController
public interface IGravityEntityController extends IUpdate
The IEntityController interface represents a controller for controlling entities in the game. It provides methods for moving the entity horizontally, jumping, coming to a stop, and retrieving the walk force and maximum velocity of the entity. This interface extends the IUpdate and IDetectGround interfaces, which provide methods for updating the controller and detecting when the entity touches the ground.
